<BR>
Oh yeah word of warning... I used this in permafrost at the site of the Archeologist (not alchemist), you know where there is that little circle of goblins off to the left side of him? Well the place was CLEARED (we had been whooping ass all day and night) and there was just one mob left. Well I snared him, and low and behold every gob within 100ft popped. Needless to say we all died. Try it some time =D<BR>
